<div class="viz-container">
<header class="viz-header">
<h1>🍃ReplicaSetElections</h1>
<p class="subtitle">HowMongoDBAchievesHighAvailabilityThroughConsensus&Failover</p>
</header>

<section class="overview-section">
<div class="overview-card">
<p>
AMongoDB<strong>replicaset</strong>isagroupof<em>mongod</em>instancesthatmaintainthesamedata.
Onememberisthe<strong>primary</strong>(handlesallwrites),therestare<strong>secondaries</strong>that
replicateviathe<em>oplog</em>—acappedcollectionofrecentwriteoperations.Whentheprimaryfails,
an<strong>election</strong>picksanewoneusingaRaft-inspiredconsensusprotocol,typicallywithin10seconds.
</p>
</div>
</section>

<!--ReplicaSetBasics-->
<section class="sim-section">
<h2>🗄️ReplicaSetBasics</h2>
<p class="section-desc">Aprimary+secondaries,connectedbyoplogreplication.Clicknodestoseetheiroplog.</p>

