<div class="explain-grid" style="margin-top:24px;">
<div class="explain-card" style="border-color:rgba(245,158,11,0.3);background:rgba(245,158,11,0.05);">
<h3>⚖️Arbiter</h3>
<p>Votesinelectionsbutholds<strong>nodata</strong>.Breakstiesineven-membersets.Usesminimalresources.</p>
<div class="verdict" style="background:rgba(245,158,11,0.15);color:#fbbf24;">Usefortie-breakingonly</div>
</div>
<div class="explain-card" style="border-color:rgba(139,92,246,0.3);background:rgba(139,92,246,0.05);">
<h3>👻HiddenMember</h3>
<p>Replicatesdatabutis<strong>invisibletoclients</strong>.Perfectforanalyticsworkloadsordedicatedbackups.</p>
<div class="verdict" style="background:rgba(139,92,246,0.15);color:#c4b5fd;">Greatforanalytics/backup</div>
</div>
<div class="explain-card" style="border-color:rgba(6,182,212,0.3);background:rgba(6,182,212,0.05);">
<h3>⏱️DelayedMember</h3>
<p>Replicateswitha<strong>timedelay</strong>(e.g.,1hourbehind).Protectionagainstaccidentaldropsorhumanerror.</p>
<div class="verdict" style="background:rgba(6,182,212,0.15);color:#67e8f9;">Insuranceagainsthumanerror</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!--OpsBestPractices-->
<section class="ops-section">
<h2>🛠️OperationalBestPractices</h2>
<div class="ops-grid">
<div class="ops-card">
<h4>📊CheckReplicaSetStatus</h4>
<code>rs.status()</code>
<p>Showseachmember'sstate,optime,heartbeatstatus,andelectioninfo.Runfirstwhentroubleshooting.</p>
</div>
<div class="ops-card">
<h4>⏱️ElectionTimeout</h4>
<code>{'settings:{electionTimeoutMillis:10000}'}</code>
<p>Default10s.Lower=fasterfailoverbutmorefalseelectionsonflakynetworks.Don'tgobelow5s.</p>
</div>
<div class="ops-card">
<h4>🏷️MemberPriority</h4>
<code>{"rs.reconfig({members:[{_id:0,priority:2}]})"}</code>
<p>Higherprioritymembersarepreferredasprimary.Setpriority:0topreventamemberfrombecomingprimary.</p>
</div>
<div class="ops-card">
<h4>📋WriteConcernMajority</h4>
<code>{"db.coll.insertOne({},{writeConcern:{w:'majority'}})"}</code>
<p>Ensureswritessurvivefailover.Slightlatencycostbutpreventsdataloss.Useforcriticaldata.</p>
</div>
<div class="ops-card">
<h4>🔍OplogSize</h4>
<code>{"rs.printReplicationInfo()"}</code>
<p>Showsoplogwindow(hoursofdata).Ifsecondariesfallbehindtheoplogwindow,theyneedfullresync.</p>
</div>
<div class="ops-card">
<h4>⚠️AvoidEvenMemberCounts</h4>
<code>Use3,5,or7members(oddnumbers)</code>
<p>Evencountsrisktiesinelections.Ifyoumustuseeven,addanarbiterforthetie-breakingvote.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>

